[In a press briefing held 17 Apr 2003 (can be accessed at:
<http://www.cdc.gov/od/oc/media/transcripts/t030417.htm>) it was
mentioned that until further testing is completed on the sensitivity
and specificity of the diagnostic tests, cases will not be
"confirmed" or "ruled out" based on laboratory testing results.
Hence, cases are defined based on clinical and epidemiological
criteria. - Mod.MPP]

